sbol:ComponentDefinition.dcterms:title: BBa_K346005
sbol:ComponentDefinition.sbh:mutableDescription: This part contains three subparts,the dsba-mbp, the mbp and the lpp-ompa-mbp. Each subpart is driven by a T7promoter along with a rbs and terminator, which will express separately in the periplasm,the cytoplasm and the membrane to bind Hg(II).
sbol:ComponentDefinition.dc:creator: Junyi Jiao, Liang Donghai, Hu Yang&Teng Xin

sbol:ComponentDefinition.dcterms:title: BBa_B0015
sbol:ComponentDefinition.sbh:mutableDescription: Double terminator consisting of BBa_B0010 and BBa_B0012
sbol:ComponentDefinition.dc:creator: Reshma Shetty

sbol:ComponentDefinition.dcterms:title: BBa_K346032
sbol:ComponentDefinition.sbh:mutableDescription: This part is a combination of T7promoter(I719005),RBS(B0034) and MBP(mercury metal binding peptide).
sbol:ComponentDefinition.dc:creator: yang hu

sbol:ComponentDefinition.dcterms:title: BBa_K346033
sbol:ComponentDefinition.sbh:mutableDescription: This part is a combination of T7promoter(BBa_I719005),RBS(B0034)and DsbA-MBP(periplasm display of mercury binding peptide)
sbol:ComponentDefinition.dc:creator: Liang Donghai Teng Xin

sbol:ComponentDefinition.dcterms:title: BBa_B0012
sbol:ComponentDefinition.sbh:mutableProvenance: Derived from the TE terminator of T7 bacteriophage between Genes 1.3 and 1.4 <genbank>V01146</genbank>.
sbol:ComponentDefinition.sbh:mutableDescription: Transcription terminator for the E.coli RNA polymerase.
sbol:ComponentDefinition.sbh:mutableNotes:
Suggested by Sri Kosuri and Drew Endy as a high efficiency terminator. The 5' end cutoff was placed immediately after the TAA stop codon and the 3' end cutoff was placed just prior to the RBS of Gene 1.4 (before AAGGAG).

Use anywhere transcription should be stopped when the gene of interest is upstream of this terminator.
sbol:ComponentDefinition.dc:creator: Reshma Shetty

sbol:ComponentDefinition.dcterms:title: BBa_B0010
sbol:ComponentDefinition.sbh:mutableDescription: Transcriptional terminator consisting of a 64 bp stem-loop.
sbol:ComponentDefinition.dc:creator: Randy Rettberg

sbol:ComponentDefinition.dcterms:title: BBa_K346003
sbol:ComponentDefinition.dcterms:description: RBS(B0032)+MBP(mercury metal binding peptide engineered from MerR)
sbol:ComponentDefinition.sbh:mutableDescription: This part is a combination of a rbs, a mbp, coding a mercury metal binding peptide egineered from MerR, and a terminator.
sbol:ComponentDefinition.dc:creator: Huyang Tengxin

sbol:ComponentDefinition.dcterms:title: BBa_K346034
sbol:ComponentDefinition.sbh:mutableDescription: This part is the combination of a T7promoter(BBa_I719005),RBS(B0034)and Lpp-OmpA+MBP(surface display of mercury binding peptide)
sbol:ComponentDefinition.dc:creator: Junyi Jiao
